    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously preserved 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This S54-powered masterpiece features the high-pressure VANOS system, fully serviced and synchronized individual throttle bodies, and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, channeling torque through a pristine limited-slip differential. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the MacPherson struts, remains in factory-spec tolerance. This is a zero-fault, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
