      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Finished in its original, high-gloss factory paint, the exterior is entirely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections, having been protected by a professional ceramic coating and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of creasing or wear, and every electronic feature\u2014from the premium surround-sound system to the advanced driver-assist features\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a smoke-free, pet-free history, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. Truly a turn-key opportunity for the most discerning buyer.",
